{"tid":1453593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非升級] 全民跳閘不合作運動","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T10:32:07.000Z","uid":142965,"like":99,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1903f746419045847ef6a943456de9004087db","tid":1453593,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"以下只講重點<br />\n<br />\nWhy? <br />\n1.  港鐵最大股東係政府 跳閘直接令政府同港鐵有收入損失 (經濟)<br />\n2.  夠和平 唔會比人打到頭破血流headshot (安全)<br />\n3.  港鐵年年都加價 去到依家咁既環境你都心甘情願比車費? (經濟/民生)<br />\n4.  同2.有關係 幫勇武派分擔 你跳閘既成本高d? 定係好似個女仔比人射爆眼成本高d? 跳多幾下 就可以打擊港共政權 你願唔願意? (道德)<br />\n<br />\nHow? <br />\n1. 事前文宣要做足 起碼有1個星期時間宣傳 同市民講解抗爭理念 訴求 成效 影響...等等 文宣清楚講明由邊日開始 號召人數夠多既話出哂黃衫人都攔唔住<br />\n2. 搵人去各個港鐵站示範 人總要有人帶頭先會做 我諗勇武派巴絲可以幫幫手 TG橡膠彈都唔驚 跳個閘應該難你地唔到<br />\n<br />\n和理非行動升級可能係抗爭新方向 以下歡迎討論  希望幫手推上熱門"},{"pid":"1bb24f463978700acfd71b6c1b3df6b22a68cd84","tid":1453593,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:46:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae42ce53492f91138bf64e5be28f6918d5855d72","tid":1453593,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701344b6894e9cc8ac9b23815c8196c559fa0ea4","tid":1453593,"uid":72354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"兄弟搭車<br />\n各有各跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbc6e479d9a91d968c6dc98e8612d7a50d73354","tid":1453593,"uid":142965,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">YOU JUMP I JUMP</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bec8cecbad8c4c73444b236a846610ca9012237b","tid":1453593,"uid":142965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB